---
title: Full of Fruit Salad Serves 1 | with Blueberry Dressing
description: Let your taste buds explode with all the flavours of the summer! Clementines, apples and spinach get tossed in a vibrant blueberry dressing. Creamy goat cheese is an elegant addition to this colourful and delicious lunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/full-of-fruit-salad-dfea73d0-0e59152f.jpg
